---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'San Diego Wedding Invitations & Save the Dates | Hummingbird Social Studio';
const description = 'Custom San Diego wedding invitations and save the dates inspired by coastal weddings, beach celebrations, garden venues, modern events, and Southern California style.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>San Diego Wedding Invitations & Save the Dates</h1>

    <p>
      Custom wedding invitation suites inspired by San Diego weddings, coastal venues,
      beach celebrations, garden ceremonies, modern events, and Southern California style.
    </p>

    <p>
      Whether you are planning a waterfront wedding, a garden celebration, a modern hotel
      wedding, or a relaxed coastal event, your invitations should feel beautiful,
      personal, and connected to your wedding day.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <div class="container">

    <h2>Inspired by San Diego Weddings</h2>

    <p>
      San Diego weddings can take many forms, from beach ceremonies and coastal receptions
      to garden venues, historic spaces, luxury hotels, private estates, and modern
      downtown celebrations.
    </p>

    <p>
      Our San Diego wedding invitations can be designed around your venue, wedding colors,
      guest experience, and overall aesthetic.
    </p>

    <h2>Popular San Diego Wedding Invitation Styles</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>San Diego wedding invitations</li>
      <li>San Diego save the dates</li>
      <li>Coastal wedding invitation suites</li>
      <li>Beach wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Southern California wedding stationery</li>
      <li>Modern wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Garden wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Destination wedding save the dates</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Designed for Coastal and Southern California Weddings</h2>

    <p>
      San Diego is a beautiful place for wedding weekends, welcome parties, rehearsal
      dinners, ceremonies, receptions, after parties, and farewell brunches.
    </p>

    <p>
      We can create cohesive stationery for the full celebration, including save the dates,
      wedding invitations, RSVP cards, details cards, itinerary cards, welcome signage,
      menus, seating charts, escort cards, and other day-of wedding paper goods.
    </p>

    <h2>Custom San Diego Wedding Stationery</h2>

    <p>
      Looking for a fully custom design? We can create San Diego wedding stationery
      that reflects your venue, your colors, your style, and the feeling of your celebration.
    </p>

    <p>
      From clean and modern to romantic, coastal, colorful, minimal, or elevated,
      each invitation suite can be customized to match your wedding vision.
    </p>

    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <h3>Do you design San Diego save the dates?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. We can create custom save the dates for San Diego weddings, coastal celebrations,
      destination weddings, and Southern California wedding weekends.
    </p>

    <h3>Can the invitations match our San Diego wedding venue?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Your invitation suite can be inspired by your venue, colors, florals,
      location, wedding style, and overall design direction.
    </p>

    <h3>Do you offer matching wedding day stationery?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Matching menus, welcome signs, seating charts, escort cards, and other
      day-of stationery can be designed to match your invitation suite.
    </p>

    <h3>Do you offer printed and digital invitations?</h3>
    <p>
      We offer both digital invitation designs and professionally printed wedding stationery.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
